# 🎮 Tic-Tac-Toe Game

This is a simple and interactive **Tic-Tac-Toe game** built using **HTML**, **CSS**, and **JavaScript**. The game features a user vs computer setup, real-time score tracking, and stylish UI with smooth interactions.


## 🛠 Technologies Used

- **HTML5** – for structure
- **CSS3** – for styling and layout
- **JavaScript (Vanilla)** – for game logic and interactivity


## 🚀 Features

- Play as "X" against a computer opponent ("O")
- Random computer moves with win/draw logic
- Stylish game board and score display
- Emoji animations on win
- Restart button to reset the game at any time


## 🖱️ How to Play

1. Open `index.html` in your browser.
2. Click on any box to make your move.
3. The computer will respond automatically.
4. The game announces the winner or a tie.
5. Click **"Restart game"** to play again.


## 📌 Notes

- The computer plays randomly – no advanced AI.
- The game highlights the winning line with color and emojis.
- Designed to be responsive and easy to read.
